    "title": "京东规则动态一览（2025年7月7日-2025年7月11日）",
    "followRuleId": "1259798898701111296",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则公示】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=638209647311982592&amp;btype=1\">《京东开放平台类目资费规则》</a> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">首档保证金阈值从0~3万调整为0~5万元。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1259478084453797888\">《京东开放平台经营类目商品阈值明细表》</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①2个类目新增设置阈值：生鲜-蛋类、生活日用-日用个护工具；②3个类目阈值变更：医疗保健-药食同源、传统滋补-养生茶饮、传统滋补-滋补营养品。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">关联规则：</span></strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1259479258473041920\">《京东开放平台个人/个体经营类目商品阈值明细表》</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1259802974834790400\">《京东好营养-多种维生素多种矿物质片品质认证质量标准》</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">修改技术要求中的功能要求及功效成分指标要求。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #3598db;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1259439390715940864&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\">《京东开放平台服务延迟报备规则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">将4种报备类型增加至6种，新增定制商品相关的报备标准，支持商家对收货地址异常的报备。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1259859855611662336\">《京东开放平台商品价格管理规则》</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①价格违规管理增加提价套取补贴场景及定义；②价格违规管理增加加收保证金、商品详情页屏蔽、限制区域销售、限制商品上架/发布、钱包冻结、类目/品牌停用等处置措施。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">关联规则：</span></strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1259859855611662336\">《京东开放平台商家违规管理总则》</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">6</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #3598db; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1259334890139291648&amp;btype=1\">《京东开放平台一物一检合规管理规则》</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">调整商品质量不合格重度瑕疵及中度瑕疵的标准定义。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则生效】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>、【新增】</strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #3598db; text-decoration-line: underline;\">《<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #3598db; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1255789833545191424\">京东开放平台大时尚品类新商激励政策（2025.7.1-2025.9.30）》</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2025</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年Q3入驻的京东开放平台时尚相关类目的商家，当GMV达到相关要求，将可获发专项激励金额，专项激励金用于广告投放。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #f8f8f9;\">2</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #f8f8f9;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #3598db; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #3598db; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1255761115896483840\">《京东开放平台商家保证金管理规则》</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background-color: #f8f8f9;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">因保证金GMV阈值合并，保证金规则举例部分，按照最新收费挡位同步调整。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>、【新增】</strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #3598db; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #3598db; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1254622809850777600&amp;btype=1\">《京东开放平台非全新商品管理规则》</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">新增非全新商品管理要求，包括非全新商品商品信息要求、违规处理措施等。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>、【修订】</strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #3598db; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #3598db; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1255847210776662016\">《京东开放平台店铺综合体验分规则》</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">五星店铺认证范围调整为在京东开放平台入驻开店的旗舰店、专卖店、专营店、卖场店店铺。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong>、【修订】</strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #3598db; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #3598db; text-decoration-line: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1255044522015068160&amp;btype=1\">《京东开放平台商品质量不合格细则》</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">调整质量违规场景定义②增加综合认定质量问题定义及对应处理措施③删除质量客诉场景④调整附则等相关表述。</span></p>",
